</span></th><th style=\"border-color:rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:0px;vertical-align:top;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);\">10.0</span></th><th style=\"border-color:rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:0px;vertical-align:top;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);\">如果用于果冻粉，按冲调倍数增加使用量</span></th></tr><tr><th style=\"border-color:rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:0px;vertical-align:top;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);\">6、可可制品、巧克力和巧克力制品（包括代可可脂巧克力及制品）以及糖果</span></th><th style=\"border-color:rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:0px;vertical-align:top;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);\">2.0</span></th><th style=\"border-color:rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:0px;vertical-align:top;\">&nbsp;</th><th style=\"border-color:rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);\">15、膨化食品</span></th><th style=\"border-color:rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:0px;vertical-align:top;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);\">10.0</span></th><th style=\"border-color:rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:0px;vertical-align:top;\">&nbsp;</th></tr><tr><th style=\"border-left-color:rgb(221, 221, 221);border-top-color:rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:0px;vertical-align:top;\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);\">7、胶基糖果</span></th><th style=\"border-left-color:rgb(221, 221, 221);border-top-color:rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:0px;vertical-align:top;\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);\">5.0</span></th><th style=\"border-left-color:rgb(221, 221, 221);border-top-color:rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:0px;vertical-align:top;\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">&nbsp;</th><th style=\"border-left-color:rgb(221, 221, 221);border-top-color:rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:0px;vertical-align:top;\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);\">16、其他（饮料浑浊剂）</span></th><th style=\"border-left-color:rgb(221, 221, 221);border-top-color:rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:0px;vertical-align:top;\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);\">10.0g/L</span></th